name: Enchiladas
instructions: Spread the frozen burritoes out onto a baking pan, then generously apply green chile sauce. Put in the oven at 350. After it has cooked for 10 minutes put the cheese on top. Once the cheese has browned a little take it out of the oven and enjoy.
note: Any flavor of el monterey burrito can be used, but the favorite is been and cheese, the yellow package I believe.
